This implementation was done using llvm-7.0.0
Download llvm-7.0.0 src code from http://releases.llvm.org/download.html
copy Project folder to <llvm-7.0.0.src>/lib/Analysis/Project
add line "add_subdirectory(Project)" to <llvm-7.0.0.src>/lib/Analysis/CMakeLists.txt
build llvm

cd into samplePrograms
change "llvm_path" variable in Makefile to show llvm-src path
run using "make file=<ll or bc file> run"

